    "text": "Interactive Plotting with Plotly\n\n\nCode\nimport plotly.express as px\nimport pandas as pd\n\ndf = pd.read_csv(\"avidya_dukkha.csv\")\n\nfig = px.scatter(\n    df,\n    x=\"psychopathology\",\n    y=\"neuroticism\",\n    color=\"avidya\",\n    hover_name=\"psychopathology\",\n    size_max=80,\n    width=1000,\n    height=600\n)\n\nfig.update_layout(\n    margin=dict(l=40, r=40, t=40, b=40)\n)"
